refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
stringopenssl_spki_export stringspkac
从编码的签名公钥和挑战导出PEM格式的公钥。

&reftitle.parameters;


   spkac



      期望一个有效的签名公钥和挑战字符串。

  &reftitle.examples;

   openssl_spki_export 范例：


      成功，返回关联的PEM格式的公钥，失败则返回 NULL.



<?php
$pkey = openssl_pkey_new('secret password');
$spkac = openssl_spki_new($pkey, 'challenge string');
$pubKey = openssl_spki_export(preg_replace('/SPKAC=/', '', $spkac));

if ($pubKey) {
    echo $pubKey;
}
?>




   openssl_spki_export example from <keygen>


      通过<keygen> 元素导出关联的PEM格式的公钥：



<?php
$spkac = openssl_spki_export(preg_replace('/SPKAC=/', '', $_POST['spkac']));
if ($spkac != NULL) {
    echo $spkac;
} else {
    echo "Extraction of pub key failed";
}
?>
<keygen name="spkac" challenge="challenge string" keytype="RSA">
